OL,3,C'We're waiting for you with open
OL,4,Carms': Mum's fresh appeal to missing
OL,5,CTaylor
OL,7,FThe mother of a 15-year-old boy who
OL,8,Fhas been missing in Barnstaple for a
OL,9,Fmonth has said she is still waiting
OL,10,Ffor him to come home 'with open arms'.
OL,12,FDevon and Cornwall Police say they are
OL,13,Fcontinuing with a significant
OL,14,Finvestigation into the disappearance
OL,15,Fof Taylor Charlton, four weeks after
OL,16,Fhe was last seen.
OL,18,FOfficers have gathered a large amount
OL,19,Fof CCTV footage which has all been
OL,20,Freviewed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
