PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780683078
OL,3,C'We're waiting for you with open
OL,4,Carms': Mum's fresh appeal to missing
OL,5,CTaylor
OL,7,FThe last confirmed sighting of Taylor
OL,8,Fis on CCTV near a footpath close to
OL,9,FTarka Leisure Centre and the Seven
OL,10,FBrethren car park, Barnstaple, at
OL,11,F10.41pm on Friday 8 May. He is seen
OL,12,Fheading in the direction of the River
OL,13,FTaw.
OL,15,FPolice say they are keen to speak to
OL,16,Fany remaining witnesses, who have not
OL,17,Fyet been in contact with police, who
OL,18,Fwere in the area at the time and may
OL,19,Fhave seen Taylor.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
