OL,3,C'We're waiting for you with open
OL,4,Carms': Mum's fresh appeal to missing
OL,5,CTaylor
OL,7,FTaylor is around 5ft 8ins tall, of
OL,8,Fmuscular build, with dark brown hair
OL,9,Fand a moustache. He was last seen
OL,10,Fwearing a bright blue fitted top,
OL,11,Fjeans and bright blue Nike shoes.
OL,13,FSenior Investigation Officer Detective
OL,14,FInspector Charlotte Heath said:
OL,15,F"Taylor is last seen on CCTV at
OL,16,F10.41pm near the footpath between the
OL,17,FTarka Leisure Centre and Seven
OL,18,FBrethren car park, Barnstaple.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
